document_data.name: Warrior Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Warrior Street''' was a road located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the mid-14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Located in the [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]] in northwest Zhentil Keep, Warrior Street ran between [[Border Street]] in the west and [[Wizards' Way]] in the east. It was intersected by [[Goblin Way]], [[Gemstone Street]], and [[Fortress Street]].
document_data.Notable Locations: A [[Zhentilar]] barracks was found at the intersection of Goblin Way with Warrior Street, and a large armory sat next to the barracks. The [[Silver Trumpet Inn]] was found at the eastern end of Warrior Street.
